data.description: Great location! Updated Pictures coming soon! Well maintained home in the quiet Pretoria Station Subdivision.  This three bedroom 2 bath home, invites you in with vaulted ceilings, wood burning fireplace and hard wood flooring in the great room. The open concept welcomes you into your beautiful newly remodeled open kitchen with granite counter tops and all the upgrades! Oversized laundry room and a huge family room! This worry free home has a new water heater, HVAC 3 years old, and the roof is 7 years old.   Enjoy the summer with your in-ground pool, newly maintenance with a new pump. Over an acre of private back yard with blueberry bushes and muscadine plants, screened porch, two work sheds one with electric and more!
